title: Gajok
description:
Story :
This story portrays the protagonist Jeong-eun a rebellious single-parent girl that is good at getting into big 
trouble. Previously arrested for robbery, she returns home after completing a two year prison term unsure of 
what will await her. Jeong's relationship with her father Ju-seok (Ju Hyun) a retired policeman has never been
on good terms and as before the two are unable to lead a meaningful conversation. When Jeong's sincere 
intentions to build up her life anew by running a beauty parlor are only met with her father's cold disbelief 
and rejection, the desperate girl tries to find other sources of support, which leads to unexpected consequences ?

Histoire :
